text.tspan: The God-men’s right to participate in God’s divinity
Includes God’s image, glorious and bright, shining forth eternally;
God’s mind! God’s glory! Expressed in Christ, the Word!
We shall reflect the image of the Son from the Lord, from the Lord,
From the Spirit of the Lord.
The God-men’s right to participate in God’s divinity
Includes God’s sonship made through Jesus Christ, God the Father’s family;
God’s sons! God’s likeness! Manifested radiantly!
We shall see Christ, yes, even as He is, and like Him, just like Him,
Just like Him we all shall be.
The God-men’s right to participate in God’s divinity
Includes being born the children of the Lord, even of the God-man gene;
God’s kind! God’s species! Constitute this realm divine!
We enter into the kingdom of the Son of His love, of His love,
Of His love for all mankind.
